<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>عَنْ أَبي قُتَيلَة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>رَوَى عَنه سَعد بْن مَسعُود.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
